</boilerplate><sections><clause id="_b37c3a35-0a24-d013-b58c-66a477462a41" unnumbered="true" obligation="normative"><p id="_50e874f9-b187-c5d3-daee-680e5cc7e9fe"><strong>HeNe laser operating on the <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
      <mrow>
        <mn>3</mn>
        <msub>
          <mi>s</mi>
          <mn>2</mn>
        </msub>
        <mo>→</mo>
        <mn>2</mn>
        <msub>
          <mi>p</mi>
          <mn>4</mn>
        </msub>
      </mrow>
    </mstyle>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>rm(3s_2 -&gt; 2p_4)</asciimath></stem> transition</strong></p>
</clause>

<clause id="_b98d4aef-6cff-c6f0-f901-b64d526943b3" obligation="normative">
<title id="_0cbaf5f2-00fc-5ab1-a272-4c13159058f5">CIPM recommended value <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ci2007" citeas="[1]"/> of the frequency</title>
<p id="_eb48d4bd-0cda-2fd3-6b42-7b3ec22b9d1a"><stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mi>f</mi>
    <mrow>
      <mo>(</mo>
      <msub>
        <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
          <mrow>
            <mi>H</mi>
            <mi>e</mi>
            <mi>N</mi>
            <mi>e</mi>
          </mrow>
        </mstyle>
        <mtext>unstabilised</mtext>
      </msub>
      <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo>=</mo>
    <mn>473.6127</mn>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_THz">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>THz</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>f(rm(HeNe)_("unstabilised"))= 473.6127 "unitsml(THz)"</asciimath></stem></p>

<p id="_a467da43-663b-a604-4bf2-fe0f7987d2d0">equivalent to</p>

<p id="_76368f96-b022-671d-a76d-aa6430f3855a"><stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mstyle mathvariant="italic">
      <mi>λ</mi>
    </mstyle>
    <mrow>
      <mo>(</mo>
      <msub>
        <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
          <mrow>
            <mi>H</mi>
            <mi>e</mi>
            <mi>N</mi>
            <mi>e</mi>
          </mrow>
        </mstyle>
        <mtext>unstabilised</mtext>
      </msub>
      <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo>=</mo>
    <mn>632.9908</mn>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_nm">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>nm</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>ii(lambda)(rm(HeNe)_("unstabilised"))= 632.9908 "unitsml(nm)"</asciimath></stem></p>

<p id="_b1f0ad10-98bb-13cc-9d82-b176ce14e527">with a relative standard uncertainty of <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mn>1.5</mn>
    <mo>×</mo>
    <msup>
      <mn>10</mn>
      <mrow>
        <mo>−</mo>
        <mn>6</mn>
      </mrow>
    </msup>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>1.5 xx 10^(-6)</asciimath></stem> applies apply to the radiation in vacuum of an unstabilized helium-neon laser operating solely on the <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
      <mrow>
        <mn>3</mn>
        <msub>
          <mi>s</mi>
          <mn>2</mn>
        </msub>
        <mo>→</mo>
        <mn>2</mn>
        <msub>
          <mi>p</mi>
          <mn>4</mn>
        </msub>
      </mrow>
    </mstyle>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>rm(3s_2 -&gt; 2p_4)</asciimath></stem> transition, independent of the isotopic mixture of the neon.</p>

<p id="_e4410fe9-ee5f-be63-fceb-bae6fe398a73"><strong>This wavelength (in vacuum) value was also recommended by CIPM 2007 as a Realization of the Definition of the Metre</strong></p>
</clause>

<clause id="_1b33c135-b786-66c3-77df-64bda7e1130c" obligation="normative">
